name: Numbers iCloud Document
summary: Learn about .NUMBERS-TEF files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Even though iCloud uses the NUMBERS-TEF extension, it shouldn't be an issue for users. When you open a spreadsheet on your Mac OS X or iOS version of Numbers, the spreadsheet will still load properly.
NOTE: Numbers spreadsheets saved on the local computer use the .NUMBERS extension.

description: Spreadsheet file created by Numbers, Apple's spreadsheet program included in the iWork suite; used as the save format when the user chooses to save the spreadsheet to iCloud.
